title: Just Get on With the Internal Affairs! – TS Demon Lord’s Management of the Demon Army - Novel Updates
tags: Beautiful Female Lead   Demon Lord   Goddesses   Male to Female   Reincarnated in Another World
author: Mumumu Mumu   Nanana Nana   六夢無　霧々   名無那 奈々
description:
When I was reborn, I was made to do 【TS】, and I was a beautiful girl demon lord!

Iori, the protagonist, is asked by a goddess to conquer a world in which 【status】,【 level】, and 【skills】 have been created by a certain evil god who loves reincarnation novels. The protagonist, Iori, is asked by a certain goddess to capture that world. And by mistake, he ends up being reincarnated as a beautiful, idealistic girl.

Well, whatever it is, it’s internal affairs. Let’s take care of the internal affairs.

Create and evolve monsters, form the strongest army, and conquer the other world!>
